# Optional: a GitHub personal access token.
# Without it, requests to the GitHub API are limited to 60/hour per IP.
# With it, the limit rises to 5,000/hour. No scopes are required for
# searching public repositories. Create one at:
# https://github.com/settings/tokens
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in the value below.
VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN=
